  "content": "v style=\"font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">&#128039;</div>\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--accent-green); margin-bottom: 12px;\">Native Ubuntu Linux</h3>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;\">\n        Docker runs natively on kernel<br>\n        No VM, no translation layer<br>\n        Direct hardware access\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-green);\">~1 GB</span><br>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted);\">OS only, Docker adds minimal</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
